  "id": "api/operators/window",
  "title": "window",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"page-actions\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/edit/master/src/internal/operators/window.ts?message=docs(operators)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L8-L112\" aria-label=\"编辑建议\" title=\"编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/tree/8.0.0-alpha.7/src/internal/operators/window.ts#L8-L112\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n  </div>\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/operators\", \"name\": \"rxjs/operators\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/operators/window\", \"name\": \"window\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/operators\">rxjs/operators</a>\n    </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"window\">window<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/operators/window#window\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">稳定</label>\n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label operator\">操作符</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  \n\n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p>Branch out the source Observable values as a nested Observable whenever\n<code>windowBoundaries</code> emits.</p>\n<p>每当 <code>windowBoundaries</code> 发出条目时，就将源 Observable 的每个值分叉成一个嵌套 Observable。</p>\n<p><span class=\"informal\">It's like <a href=\"api/operators/buffer\"><code>buffer</code></a>, but emits a nested Observable\ninstead of an array.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"informal\">类似于 <a href=\"api/operators/buffer\"><code>buffer</code></a>，但它会发送一个嵌套的 Observable 而非数组。</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"/assets/images/marble-diagrams/window.png\" width=\"100%\" alt=\"window marble diagram\"></p>\n<p>Returns an Observable that emits windows of items it collects from the source\nObservable. The output Observable emits connected, non-overlapping\nwindows. It emits the current window and opens a new one whenever the\n<code>windowBoundaries</code> emits an item. <code>windowBoundaries</code> can be any type that\n<code><a href=\"api/index/type-alias/ObservableInput\" class=\"code-anchor\">ObservableInput</a></code> accepts. It internally gets converted to an Observable.\nBecause each window is an Observable, the output is a higher-order Observable.</p>\n<p>返回一个 Observable，它会发出一些从源 Observable 收集来的条目的窗口。输出 Observable 会发送已连接的、不重叠的窗口。只要 <code>windowBoundaries</code> 这个 Observable 发出了一个条目，它就会发送当前窗口，并打开一个新窗口。因为每个窗口都是一个 Observable，所以其输出是一个高阶 Observable。</p>\n<h2 id=\"example\">Example<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/operators/window#example\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<h2 id=\"例子\">例子<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/operators/window#例子\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p>In every window of 1 second each, emit at most 2 click events</p>\n<p>在每个间隔 1 秒的窗口中，最多发送 2 个点击事件</p>\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\nimport { <a href=\"api/index/function/fromEvent\" class=\"code-anchor\">fromEvent</a>, <a href=\"api/index/function/interval\" class=\"code-anchor\">interval</a>, <a href=\"api/index/function/window\" class=\"code-anchor\">window</a>, <a href=\"api/index/function/map\" class=\"code-anchor\">map</a>, <a href=\"api/index/function/take\" class=\"code-anchor\">take</a>, <a href=\"api/index/function/mergeAll\" class=\"code-anchor\">mergeAll</a> } from 'rxjs';\n\nconst clicks = <a href=\"api/index/function/fromEvent\" class=\"code-anchor\">fromEvent</a>(document, 'click');\nconst sec = <a href=\"api/index/function/interval\" class=\"code-anchor\">interval</a>(1000);\nconst result = clicks.pipe(\n  <a href=\"api/index/function/window\" class=\"code-anchor\">window</a>(sec),\n  <a href=\"api/index/function/map\" class=\"code-anchor\">map</a>(win => win.pipe(<a href=\"api/index/function/take\" class=\"code-anchor\">take</a>(2))), // <a href=\"api/index/function/take\" class=\"code-anchor\">take</a> at most 2 emissions <a href=\"api/index/function/from\" class=\"code-anchor\">from</a> each <a href=\"api/index/function/window\" class=\"code-anchor\">window</a>\n  <a href=\"api/index/function/mergeAll\" class=\"code-anchor\">mergeAll</a>()                     // flatten the Observable-of-Observables\n);\nresult.subscribe(x => console.log(x));\n</code-example>\n<p></p>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <a href=\"api/index/function/window\" class=\"code-anchor\">window</a>&#x3C;T>(windowBoundaries: <a href=\"api/index/type-alias/ObservableInput\" class=\"code-anchor\">ObservableInput</a>&#x3C;any>): <a href=\"api/index/interface/OperatorFunction\" class=\"code-anchor\">OperatorFunction</a>&#x3C;T, <a href=\"api/index/class/Observable\" class=\"code-anchor\">Observable</a>&#x3C;T>></code-example>\n\n\n\n  <h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">参数</h4>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"windowBoundaries\"></a>\n        <code>windowBoundaries</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code><a href=\"api/index/type-alias/ObservableInput\" class=\"code-anchor\">ObservableInput</a>&#x3C;any></code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      <p>        An <code><a href=\"api/index/type-alias/ObservableInput\" class=\"code-anchor\">ObservableInput</a></code> that completes the\nprevious window and starts a new window.</p>\n<p>一个 Observable，当它发出值时，就会完成前一个窗口并启动一个新窗口。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n  <h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值\">返回值</h4>\n  <p><code><a href=\"api/index/interface/OperatorFunction\" class=\"code-anchor\">OperatorFunction</a>&#x3C;T, <a href=\"api/index/class/Observable\" class=\"code-anchor\">Observable</a>&#x3C;T>></code>: A function that returns an Observable of windows, which are\nObservables emitting values of the source Observable.</p>\n<p>一个函数，它会返回一个以窗口为条目的 Observable，每个窗口都是一个 Observable，发送的是来自源 Observable 的值。</p>\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">参见<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/operators/window#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n  \n    <li><a href=\"api/operators/windowCount\"><code>windowCount</code></a>\n</li>\n    <li><a href=\"api/operators/windowTime\"><code>windowTime</code></a>\n</li>\n    <li><a href=\"api/operators/windowToggle\"><code>windowToggle</code></a>\n</li>\n    <li><a href=\"api/operators/windowWhen\"><code>windowWhen</code></a>\n</li>\n    <li><a href=\"api/operators/buffer\"><code>buffer</code></a>\n</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/operators\n - api/operators/buffer\n - api/operators/windowCount\n - api/operators/windowTime\n - api/operators/windowToggle\n - api/operators/windowWhen\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/index/class/Observable\n - api/index/function/from\n - api/index/function/fromEvent\n - api/index/function/interval\n - api/index/function/map\n - api/index/function/mergeAll\n - api/index/function/take\n - api/index/function/window\n - api/index/interface/OperatorFunction\n - api/index/type-alias/ObservableInput\n - api/operators\n - api/operators/buffer\n - api/operators/window#example\n - api/operators/window#see-also\n - api/operators/window#window\n - api/operators/window#例子\n - api/operators/windowCount\n - api/operators/windowTime\n - api/operators/windowToggle\n - api/operators/windowWhen\n - https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/edit/master/src/internal/operators/window.ts?message=docs(operators)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L8-L112\n - https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/tree/8.0.0-alpha.7/src/internal/operators/window.ts#L8-L112\n-->"
